#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/spring-data-rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`GET /fruits` - lists all entities or returns a page if `PagingAndSortingRepository` or `JpaRepository` is used."
msgstr "`GET /fruits` - 列出所有实体；若使用了 `PagingAndSortingRepository` 或 `JpaRepository` ，则返回分页结果。"

