msgstr "`PUT /fruits/:id` - 更新现有实体，或创建一个具有指定 ID 的新实体（如果实体定义允许的话）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/spring-data-rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`DELETE /fruits/:id` - deletes an entity by ID."
msgstr "`DELETE /fruits/:id` - 根据 ID 删除一个实体。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/spring-data-rest.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"There are two supported data types: `application/json` and `application/hal+json`.\n"
"The former is used by default, but it is highly recommended to specify which one you prefer with an `Accept` header."
msgstr "支持两种数据类型： `application/json` 和 `application/hal+json` 。默认使用前者，但强烈建议您通过 `Accept` 头字段指定首选的数据类型。"

